<div id="review_1525963706" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1525963706" />
    <a title="James Perry" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/47656166-james-perry"><img alt="James Perry" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1525963706?book_show_action=true">Jan 26, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="James Perry" class="user" itemprop="url" name="James Perry" href="/user/show/47656166-james-perry">James Perry</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover " href="/book/show/16093260-for-the-love-of-the-game">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1525963706" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17795954890627746039">I found this book an exceptional one mainly because of how personal it got with Jordan. Not only did he give you an inside look at his emotions, but it also brought you inside the locker room with the players and almost made you feel like you had a personal connection with both him and the players. I recommend this book to anyone who is looking for a genuine sports story.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


